props.description:
Metadata filter expression to select vectors to delete. Examples:
• {"genre": {"$eq": "documentary"}}
• {"year": {"$gt": 2019}}
• {"$and": [{"genre": "comedy"}, {"year": {"$gte": 2020}}]}

Filter to apply using vector metadata. Examples:
• {"genre": {"$eq": "documentary"}}
• {"year": {"$gt": 2019}}
• {"$and": [{"genre": {"$in": ["comedy", "drama"]}}, {"year": {"$gte": 2020}}]}
